messages.content: I must take my leave, Miss Bennet. The estate requires my attention.
Come now, Mr. Darcy, a man of your consequence must employ nothing but the finest automation tools. Or do you still prefer manual data entry?
I must confess, the OpenFn integrations have transformed our estate management beyond measure.
The automated data flows have reduced out clerical staff by three persons, and we now employ them as teachers and event organisers for the Lambton community.
Indeed, Mr. Darcy. May your workflow automations bring you much efficiency.
